item.title: [HBASE-16892] Use TableName instead of String in SnapshotDescription
item.description:
mostly find & replace work:
deprecate the SnapshotDescription constructors with the String argument in favor of the TableName ones.
Replace the TableName.valueOf() around with the new getTableName()
Replace the TableName.getNameAsString() by just passing the TableName
item.summary: Use TableName instead of String in SnapshotDescription

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
